sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (Player)
    participant CP as Control Plane
    participant DRM as License Svc
    participant OCA as Open Connect (CDN)
    participant Org as Origin (fallback)

    Note over C,Org: Playback start -> ABR chunk streaming
    C->>CP: POST /playback/start {title_id, profile}
    CP->>CP: auth + geo check + rights
    CP-->>C: manifest URL + session token + edge list
    C->>DRM: request license (device id + token)
    DRM-->>C: short-lived decryption key
    C->>OCA: GET manifest (DASH/HLS)
    OCA-->>C: variants ladder (240p..4K)
    Note over C: client measures bandwidth, picks bitrate
    loop chunk-by-chunk ABR (4-10s chunks)
        C->>OCA: GET chunk @ chosen bitrate
        alt OCA has chunk (pre-positioned)
            OCA-->>C: encrypted chunk
        else cache miss
            OCA->>Org: fill from origin
            Org-->>OCA: chunk
            OCA-->>C: encrypted chunk
        end
        C->>C: decrypt + decode + measure throughput
        Note over C: switch up if buffer healthy, down if dipping
    end
    C-)CP: heartbeat (position, buffer health)
